@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ifdsem(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.10)) + 0.09)
    v1 = wp.abs((v2 * (tmp + 0.72 / tmp + 0.20)))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.exp(tmp + 0.05) - v1))
    v0 = (wp.exp(0.68) - ((tmp + 0.71 - v1 + 0.09) * 0.36))
    v2 = (v1 + v0)
    data[tid] = v0
